      "acceptanceCriteria": "Force residuals converge to < 1e-5 relative norm; energy balance error < 0.1% for all load steps.",
      "rationale": "Nonlinear solution convergence was monitored across all load steps. Force residuals achieved < 1e-6 relative norm and energy balance error remained below 0.05%. No divergence events were recorded across the 11-construct ensemble."
