      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent model review by second analyst; documented modeling protocol with checklist completion.",
      "rationale": "A documented FEA modeling protocol with 47-item checklist was followed for each construct model. An independent analyst reviewed boundary condition assignments, material property mappings, and contact definitions. No use errors were identified during the review."
