      "rationale": "The validation constructs used production-representative non-cannulated 7.5 mm screws identical to those in the COU. ASTM F1717 test geometry (35 mm offset, UHMWPE block) and loading rate (5 mm/min quasi-static) directly replicate the COU conditions. No geometric surrogates or scaled models were employed, ensuring high relevance of the validation activities to the COU."
    }
